{"tid":1208160,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青年新政呼籲：圍魏救趙","createTime":"2019-06-12T08:59:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-12T10:09:38.000Z","uid":389,"like":34,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ef150832f0a7850e9a21c5706dd18c30fada235e","tid":1208160,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T08:59:13.000Z","msg":"圍魏救趙<br />\n<br />\n6月9日的103萬香港人重新集結，陸陸續續來到金鐘將立法會包圍，向林鄭月娥的獨裁政權發出怒哮。可是單單集結，是遠遠不足夠令專權無道的林鄭讓步。一如所料，布袋彈、催淚煙近距射向示威者，根本具有殺人意圖，令多名抗爭者重創。<br />\n<br />\n塞路動搖不了政權，我們就堵塞主要幹道。為了保護金鐘一帶的青年人，為了保護香港的未來，不合作運動將全面展開，癱瘓全香港。林鄭暴虐政權，盡速收回惡法! If we burn, you burn with us!<br />\n<br />\n香港人，今仗我地許勝不許敗，只要堅持，我地一定會贏返一次!<br />\n<br />\n======<br />\n轉載網上消息<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/68jUeA1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F68jUeA1.png&h=5a81f31a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e88fb9976239e53342051316e9cb1b188adff98d","tid":1208160,"uid":36178,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:01:37.000Z","msg":"青政吹雞, 全民出動"},{"pid":"154777c28fdeef226934a14acd83cc8b35b34d28","tid":1208160,"uid":173849,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:03:03.000Z","msg":"遊擊反包圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad65a7a238e0919bd37beadc7376262e867b0442","tid":1208160,"uid":389,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e88fb9976239e53342051316e9cb1b188adff98d","tid":1208160,"uid":36178,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:01:37.000Z","msg":"青政吹雞, 全民出動"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:04:44.000Z","msg":"明明係「癱瘓香港」<br />\n唔知點解叫圍魏救趙"},{"pid":"9cef5f5b57def2fbc55b22fdc07264133ce6a851","tid":1208160,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88c67ba318b090e931c12e8ccb6a1d3c2461a81f"